{"tid":544833,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"泰利以錦標反擊曼聯借將","createTime":"2018-01-30T02:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T10:48:30.000Z","uid":333,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b19fdb86fe0df9c5b4157524ef132d14262fd885","tid":544833,"uid":333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=K0iBZ6rl8Rud6QRIZBRUzgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=d05603bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】面對曼聯借將杜安沙比的挖苦，效力阿士東維拉的泰利決定以個人錦標數目反擊。<br />\n<br />\n去年在領隊摩連奴身上取得個人首次一隊上陣機會的20歲小將杜安沙比（Axel Tuanzebe），為了爭取更多上陣機會，日前正式從曼聯外借至英冠的阿士東維拉，並有機會在維拉明日對錫菲聯的賽事中首次上陣。<br />\n<br />\n不過這名小將在社交網絡Instagram的一張照片，卻點起火頭。照片中看見杜安沙比的訓練球衣跑步，後面則有模糊的泰利（John Terry）在背景，杜安沙比留言「後衛中最前的一個」，並特別標籤泰利。<br />\n<br />\n結果泰利當然不客氣，以17個冠軍logo回應，數目剛剛是他個人職業生涯上贏得的錦標數目，當中包括兩次為車路士贏下的社區盾。最終杜安沙比可能知道玩過火，已刪除有關泰利的標籤。"},{"pid":"d7274cee7808aed7a1417e16ac02fa6e8cd6c10f","tid":544833,"uid":57035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"老屎忽"},{"pid":"243c200cfb69e9ba2b20e02fa7b2cee571ab1224","tid":544833,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://metrouk2.files.wordpress.com/2018/01/tuanzebe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmetrouk2.files.wordpress.com%2F2018%2F01%2Ftuanzebe.jpg&h=e4b9ddf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93868782a36b51d023669097da87c78b3292ee94","tid":544833,"uid":143667,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"nigga 真係無撚腦"},{"pid":"928254fe445fb4b1639ea6d35b21d0d00b8a289d","tid":544833,"uid":6782,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:04:32.000Z","msg":"好明顯係玩 寫到世界大戰咁 英國報紙佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06d930785e89e95c4